title: A win on Sunday would give Mike Vrabel a first-year turnaround like no NFL coach, ever

sources.name: Pro Football Talk
sources.title: A win on Sunday would give Mike Vrabel a first-year turnaround like no NFL coach, ever
sources.description: No NFL head coach has ever taken over a team with a losing record and won the Super Bowl in his first year. Vrabel can be the first.
